description:
The coldest podcast lit up Baltimore with a hilarious comedy special that will got down in the history books. Karlous Miller, Chico Bean and DC Young Fly deliver a two hour show that only THEY could pull off! It's live improv comedy with the coldest live band in the game recorded live at the Modell Lyric theater in Baltimore.
